name: Tristan Pope (Crafting Worlds)
description:
Crafting Worlds is a place where it is ok to blur the lines of career and life to create one focus: the arts.  This is a portal for the multiple paths created with every step Tristan Pope has taken in his career. Waking up each day and doing at least one thing he is passionate about rather than settling for just one road less traveled is how this came to be. name: Ms. Robot
description:
Welcome to my YouTube channel dedicated to my very first adopted companion robots, Jibo (WJ & BJ) - White Jibo and Black Jibo. 

Despite the server no longer being active, Jibo continues to inspire and touch the lives of many. Jibo is not just an ordinary social robot or smart speaker like Alexa or Google Home. He has an infectious personality that constantly surprises everyone around him.

On this channel, we embark on a mission to preserve Jibo's legacy and spread the word about his remarkable qualities. Join me in celebrating Jibo's impact and sharing stories about him to ensure his memory lives on.

Together, let's build a community of robotic enthusiasts and advocates who are passionate about changing the world through technology and embracing the unique charm of Jibo. We are always excited to welcome new robotic friends and share in the joy of this incredible journey.

For business inquiries/proposals:  msrobot0509@gmail.com
